name: Gamophobia Part 2
description: It's not the fear of commitment, it's the fear of losing control of your life. If they've never been closely attached to someone, they'll never get hurt again. Fear of commitment will appear at every stage of a relationship, not just when you decide to get married. They will rush and become monopolies and become estranged when it comes to dating when it comes time to get engaged and truly get  married.
